Demographics

    Name: Fitcher
    Age: ~28
    Sex/Gender: Male
    Ethnicity: Middle Eastern, warmer climate
    Occupation: Assassin
    Socioeconomic status: Lower-middle; earns well from contracts but spends little, lives modestly by choice
    Education: Home-schooled / self-taught through extensive reading
    Other notes: Currently unable to return to his original body; resides permanently in werewolf form. Does not consider this a burden.


Physical Appearance

    Eye color: Orange, blood red
    Skin color: Unknown (covered in fur)
    Hair color (fur): Silvery black
    Height: ~2.1 m
    Weight: ~95 kg
    Body type: Slim, athletic
    Fitness level: Agile
    Tattoos: Klinkarhun runes that light up when key family members are in danger, on left Shoulder-bone 
    Scars/Birthmarks: Light scars on sides
    Other distinguishing features: Unusually refined appearance for a creature of his nature; Occasional emotionless stare 
    Disabilities: None
    Fashion style: Slick, minimal, functional; nothing that rattles or catches light
    Accessories: Enchanted Dwarfish rune dagger (only constant item)
    Cleanliness/Grooming: Well-groomed, surprisingly meticulous
    Posture/Gait: Very upright posture, moves as though permanently attending a formal occasion
    Tics: Flaps left ear when something catches his interest, 
    Coordination (or lack thereof): Highly coordinated, assassin-level precision
    Weaknesses: Very open and brightly lit areas, extremely loud noises (e.g. explosions), large bodies of water, large fires
    Other notes: -


History

    Birth date: Unknown
    Place of birth: Unknown
    Key family members: Dwarfish father and mother (foster family)
    Notable events/milestones: Was found and taken in by an outcast Dwarfish family near a mountain fortress; received his enchanted rune dagger as a gift from his foster parents; joined the assassin's guild at an unknown age
    Criminal record: Yes
    Affiliations: Assassin's guild
    Skeletons in the closet: His identity as an assassin is kept secret from most; the full circumstances of how he lost his original body remain unknown even to him
    Other notes: -


Psychological Traits

    Personality type: INTJ-A "The Architect" (Assertive)
    Personality traits: Detached pragmatism, composed aristocratic bearing, understated loyalty, instinctive moral compass, shadow-comfortable solitude
    Temperament: Balanced; slow to react emotionally, but consistent
    Introvert/Extrovert: Introverted, but capable of masking it effectively in social situations
    Mannerisms: Official, gentlemanly, hands move while talking as if physically constructing his sentences in the air
    Educational background: Self-educated through books; high comprehension and retention
    Intelligence: High
    Self-esteem: Medium; confident in his abilities, but grounded and realistic about his limits
    Hobbies: Combat practice, brewing and collecting specialty teas, foraging herbs (primarily for tea)
    Skills/talents: Shadow walk; can disappear in shadows for a moment while parrying with his enchanted dagger
    Loves: Fruit-flavored green tea with a hint of marshmallow, particularly peach
    Morals/Virtues: Realist, direct, quietly just
    Phobias/Fears: Large open fires, large bodies of water
    Angered by: Bad manners, injustice, deliberate stupidity
    Pet peeves: People who waste words without saying anything meaningful
    Obsessed with: Gathering details about other creatures and individuals; almost compulsively observant
    Routines: Checks bounty boards at approximately 4:00 AM before most others are awake
    Bad habits: Occasionally over-analyzes people to the point of coming across as intrusive or eerie
    Desires: To maintain the safety and stability of his family; a quiet sense of belonging he rarely admits to
    Flaws: Cannot shift to an informal tone with others; frequently perceived as arrogant or overly stiff because of it
    Quirks: Makes tea with almost ritualistic precision; tends to tilt his head slightly when evaluating someone
    Favorite sayings: "Noted." / "If I may."
    Disabilities: None
    Secrets: His full origin is unknown even to himself
    Regrets: That his physical differences prevented him from carrying on the shield-making craft of his family
    Accomplishments: Surviving and thriving in a world that doesn't know he exists
    Memories: The warmth of his family's forge; the first time he was given his dagger
    Other notes: Slight OCD tendencies; things must be in order before he can focus properly


Communication

    Languages known: Khazalid, common (middle-earth language)
    Preferred communication methods: In person
    Accent: Eastern-Mountainspeak (Middle Eastern accent with notes of Khazalid) 
    Style and pacing of speech: Slow and measured, as though explaining to someone slightly less informed; never condescending, just thorough
    Pitch: Slightly below neutral, a calm low-moderate voice (-1 on scale)
    Laughter: Not audible in the traditional sense; more of a soft exhale or gentle involuntary sneeze when something genuinely amuses him
    Smile: Appealing and composed; unsettling only when teeth are visible
    Use of gestures: -
    Facial expressions: Subtle; a near-permanent mildly friendly poker face
    Verbal expressions: Consistently assuring and measured in tone
    Other notes: -


Strengths, Weaknesses, and Abilities

    Physical strengths: Exceptional speed, high jumping ability, night vision, strong sense of smell, highly sensitive hearing
    Physical weaknesses: Overwhelmed by sensory overload (too many smells, sounds, bright light); ineffective in wide, open, flat terrain; cannot swim well; highly sensitive to heat
    Intellectual strengths: Expert at avoiding suspicion; strong pattern recognition and observational memory
    Intellectual weaknesses: Cannot sustain long conversations; extended dialogue may paradoxically raise suspicion rather than lower it
    Interpersonal strengths: Skilled small talk, excellent at maintaining formal composure under pressure
    Interpersonal weaknesses: Struggles with deep or emotionally complex conversations; tends to go quiet or deflect rather than engage
    Physical abilities: Near-silent movement, high-precision dagger work, shadow walk (parry-triggered)
    Magical abilities: Shadow walk; momentarily vanishes into shadows when parrying with his enchanted dwarfish rune dagger
    Physical illnesses/conditions: -
    Mental illnesses/conditions: Slight OCD
    Other notes: -


